class lihzahrd.enums.RLEEncoding¶

How the RLE compression is encoded.

DOUBLE_BYTE = 2¶

The read data refers to 256-4800 tiles (2 bytes).

NO_COMPRESSION = 0¶

The read data refers to a single tile.

SINGLE_BYTE = 1¶

The read data refers to 2-255 tiles (1 byte).
